{"tid":1300581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"快啲買寶礦力","createTime":"2019-07-09T11:52:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T13:21:54.000Z","uid":244242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4f1f1301164539ba4c0ec55d0a0ab0dc359ae738","tid":1300581,"uid":244242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:52:55.000Z","msg":"寶礦力決定撤回TVB廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1300186\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1300186</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今次抵制tvb行動算係踏出左第一步 <br />\n但係<span style=\"color: red;\">未完</span> 我地重要比其他公司知道<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地示威者既力量係幾咁龐大<br />\n跟tvb 落廣告就<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">等收皮</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">同示威者一齊抵制tvb就大把着數</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以我地要買寶礦力支持抵制tvb行動</span>"},{"pid":"4db7773eefa0c6199ff569d0671eeda9990d47d6","tid":1300581,"uid":244242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:53:22.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"965041c70ef5cc32284d2791afcda196ec998e41","tid":1300581,"uid":174829,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T05:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b2314d2802070ab724377c4098ed049027b148","tid":1300581,"uid":240869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:21:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}